--- a/qtwebengine/src/3rdparty/chromium/sandbox/linux/syscall_broker/syscall_dispatcher.cc.orig	1970-01-01 08:00:00.000000000 +0800
+++ b/qtwebengine/src/3rdparty/chromium/sandbox/linux/syscall_broker/syscall_dispatcher.cc.orig	2026-03-16 19:40:07.000000000 +0800
